[l] Überraschung: Die Geheimdienstberichte ueber ISIS wurden auf dem Weg durch die Hierarchien bis hin zu Obama massiv geschoent.The analysts have accused senior-level leaders, including the director of intelligence and his deputy in CENTCOM, of changing their analyses to be more in line with the Obama administration’s public contention that the fight against ISIS and al Qaeda is making progress. The analysts take a more pessimistic view about how military efforts to destroy the groups are going.Hipp Hipp Hurra, alles ist super, alles ist wunderbar! (Danke, Joerg)
